data.description: Assume the VA loan on this adorable home near the end of a deadend street. It has alley access to take advantage of the large back yard for RV parking, boats and toys. The 12'x24' detached garage has plenty of room to park the car or to use as a shop. Enter the home from the front door into cozy living room and kitchen. There is also one bedroom and a bathroom on the main level. The downstairs has 9' ceilings, a large family room and 2 bedrooms as well as under the stairs storage. Stop by and take a look at this cute home close to everything in Payette. Still doing some touch-up painting.
